laboratory_examinations.procedure_name: MRI of Head with and without contrast
laboratory_examinations.findings: Stable appearance of extra-axial enhancing mass abutting the posteroinferior aspect of the right temporal bone measuring 2 x 1.5 cm; stable en plaque meningiomas measuring 13 x 16 mm at the right frontal convexity; extensive periventricular and deep white matter high signal intensity consistent with chronic microvascular ischemia; encephalomalacia within the right cerebellum.
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: Stable appearance of lesions compared to previous imaging.
